Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:51.82,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}起立！敬禮！鎖定！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:56.72,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}曾經想著總有人會解決
