Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:04.96,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}然而
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:10.25,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}Mr.teacher請告訴不成熟的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:15.75,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}何時才能擊倒你這個不落的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:21.25,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}只要挑戰 可能性是half＆half
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:26.24,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}Mr.teacher請看著迷茫的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:31.49,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}為了你比任何人都認真學習
